message.content: This paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as the paper proposes a neural network approach for generating question-answer pairs from Wikipedia articles.
